title: Countercharm
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki
xpcost: 1

When you perform your music, you can disrupt mind-influencing effects on yourself and your allies. As long as you continue to play music, you and any friendly creatures you choose who can hear you within 30 feet of you have [[advantage]] to resist any magical effects that would influence their behavior, such as [[charm]] or [[cause fear]].